      <title>try...catch</title>
      <link href="/2022/09/27/trycatch/"/>
      <url>/2022/09/27/trycatch/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="catch-和作用域"><a href="#catch-和作用域" class="headerlink" title="catch 和作用域"></a>catch 和作用域</h2><p>🤔 思考: 以下表达式输出？</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">let</span> x;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">try</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">throw</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">Error</span>();</span><br><span class="line">&#125; <span class="keyword">catch</span> (x) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    x = <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="variable language_">console</span>.<span class="title function_">log</span>(x);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable language_">console</span>.<span class="title function_">log</span>(x)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>答案解析：</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 考察 catch和作用域</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// catch块指定一个标识符（下面为x），该标识符保存由throw语句指定的值。</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// catch块是唯一的，因为输入catch块时，javascript会创建此标识符，并将其添加到当前作用域。</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 标识符仅在catch块执行时存在；catch块执行完成后，标识符不再可用。</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 答案 1 undefined</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">let</span> x;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">try</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">throw</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">Error</span>();</span><br><span class="line">&#125; <span class="keyword">catch</span> (x) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// x仅在catch块中可用</span></span><br><span class="line">    x = <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="variable language_">console</span>.<span class="title function_">log</span>(x); <span class="comment">// 输出 1</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable language_">console</span>.<span class="title function_">log</span>(x) <span class="comment">// x从未赋值，输出 undefined</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
